| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5841 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b3ad0d86-ce5d-5d85-b6ac-a0c23eca04f3"
